5
00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:11.020
Reliability, maintenance, and maintainability are fundamental to almost every activity involving engineered and manufactured systems.

6
00:00:11.020 --> 00:00:23.812
Their domains of application are extremely broad, ranging from industrial plants, aircraft engines, and mining equipment to transportation systems, energy infrastructure, and medical devices.

7
00:00:23.812 --> 00:00:31.876
As a result, R and M problems arise at multiple levels of complexity and in virtually every asset-intensive industry.

